            <formatted-text>
              <run>Notes:
- Sources: CDC WONDER and US Census Bureau
- Forecast Method: Race-specific linear regression
- National-level aggregation
- Predictions assume continuation of historical trends</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
