          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='4300' id='19' type-v2='text' w='98814' x='593' y='60900'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='2' fontsize='16'>At today&apos;s trajectory, Black and White maternal mortality rates won&apos;t reach parity for </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='2' fontcolor='#bf1341' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='16' italic='true'>three centuries</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='2' fontsize='16'>. By that time, the maternal mortality rate is forecasted to be </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='2' fontcolor='#6c0c3d' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='16'>11.8</run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='2' fontsize='16'>.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
